OL,3,CBurglars jailed after threatening man,
OL,4,C72, with a hammer in his home
OL,6,FTwo men have been jailed for forcing
OL,7,Ftheir way into a 72-year-old's home
OL,8,Fand threatening him with weapons.
OL,10,FKirk Scotland, 39, and Brian
OL,11,FCrutchley, 33, barged into the
OL,12,Fproperty in Middlesbrough on 17
OL,13,FSeptember 2023 armed with weapons
OL,14,Fincluding a hammer.
OL,16,FThey held the victim down, searching
OL,17,Fhis wallet and pockets before stealing
OL,18,Fsome items of furniture.
