OL,6,FSix days later, the pair returned to
OL,7,Fthe property and let themselves in
OL,8,Fwith a key they had taken. Whilst
OL,9,Finside, they again went through the
OL,10,Fvictim's pockets before leaving.
OL,12,FThe incidents were reported to
OL,13,FCleveland Police and the pair were
OL,14,Farrested amid an investigation.
OL,16,FScotland, from Middlesbrough, and
OL,17,FCrutchley, from Hartlepool, were both
OL,18,Fcharged with burglary and robbery.
