OL,3,CBurglars jailed after threatening man,
OL,4,C72, with a hammer in his home
OL,6,FScotland pleaded guilty to the charges
OL,7,Fon 25 March 2024. Crutchley initially
OL,8,Fpleaded not guilty to both charges but
OL,9,Fwas found guilty of burglary after a
OL,10,Ftrial at Teesside Crown Court.
OL,12,FOn Thursday 28 March, they both
OL,13,Fappeared at Teesside Crown Court for
OL,14,Fsentencing where Scotland was jailed
OL,15,Ffor seven years and Crutchley was
OL,16,Fjailed for three years and four months.
OL,18,FBoth Crutchley and Scotland were also
OL,19,Fissued with lifetime restraining
OL,20,Forders to protect the victim.
