OL,6,FInvestigating officer PC Corey Gosling
OL,7,Fsaid: "This was a terrifying
OL,8,Fexperience for the victim who showed
OL,9,Fan amazing amount of courage to attend
OL,10,Fcourt and give evidence.
OL,12,F"I hope the victim can take some
OL,13,Fcomfort in the fact that Scotland and
OL,14,FCrutchley are now serving their
OL,15,Fcustodial sentences and are unable to
OL,16,Fcause harm to anyone else.
